import com.eviware.soapui.support.GroovyUtils
File empFile = new File("C:\\Users\\lokesh.kondepudi\\Documents\\Lokesh\\soap-ui\\empData.txt")
def groovyUtils = new GroovyUtils(context) String age,department,id,name String ageRes,deptRes,idRes,nameRes def lineData def reqXmlHolder, resXmlHolder
empFile.eachLine{ line-> lineData = line.split(" ") age = lineData[0] department = lineData[1] id = lineData[2] name = lineData[3]
reqXmlHolder = groovyUtils.getXmlHolder("getEmpDetailsSOAP#Request") reqXmlHolder["//typ:employeeName"]=name reqXmlHolder.updateProperty()
testRunner.testCase.getTestStepByName('getEmpDetailsSOAP').run(testRunner,context) resXmlHolder = groovyUtils.getXmlHolder("getEmpDetailsSOAP#Response")
ageRes = resXmlHolder["//ns:age"] deptRes = resXmlHolder["//ns:department"] idRes = resXmlHolder["//ns:id"] nameRes = resXmlHolder["//ns:name"]
log.info "$ageRes, $deptRes, $idRes, $nameRes" log.warn "$age, $department, $id, $name"
// compare the values assert age == ageRes assert department == deptRes assert id == idRes assert name == nameRes }
